Thanks for checking out my LinkedIn profile. I have a diverse design and user experience background, working for companies like Amazon and Jet. I'm currently doing user experience work for ADP in the healthcare compliance space.

I'm always looking to connect with top notch people and companies, so feel free to reach out.

Skills:
- Data-driven user research, testing, and surveying
- Early product prototyping and interface wire-framing
- User interface and visual design (including style guidance and visual branding)
- Product management and requirements documentation
- Team oversight, task delegation, and project accountability
- Tech implementation (browser and device testing, QA, DevOps, data schema planning, deployment strategy, infrastructure monitoring)
- Conversion optimization, analytics, and A/B testing
- HCI, human-centered design, Lean, Scrum, Kanban
- Adobe Creative Cloud (Photoshop, Illustrator), Sketch, InVision, Axure, Balsamiq
- HTML, CSS, SASS / LESS, Bootstrap, Compass
- Ruby, node, PHP, Laravel, nginx, MySQL, REST / API, webhooks
